text: Ivakinsky Karyer () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Vsevolodo- Vilvenskoye Urban Settlement, Alexandrovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 331 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 5.5 km north-east from Vsevolodo-Vilva. == References == Category:Rural localities in Alexandrovsky District
title: Ivakinsky Karyer
